Do you have any idea how deep you have to fight in chardok to get all 55+ mobs?<br>
<br>
Let me explain it for ya.  It's past the zone in.  It's past the fort, it's past the bridge..hell, even at the castle entrance, there are still blues to 55.<br>
<br>
Take your average pickup group, and do a goddamned Bathezid raid, because that's what you're asking them to do now.  First off, sometimes I don't feel like devoting that much goddamned energy to gaining some halfassed decent XP in a @#%$ VIDEO GAME.  Secondly, fighting in a place that requires a COFFIN CORPSE RETRIEVAL if you screw up is not worth anyone's time for the mass XP grind.<br>
<br>
If you wanna log on for an hour or 2 and just knock off a yellow AA or 2, right now, you're better off getting an extra 2 hours of sleep.  I don't want to have to amass a balanced full group every goddamned time I want to XP...and don't tell me I still have the option to do small group stuff, because I don't.  A yellow an hour was fine, anything less is a waste of time.<br>
<br>
